sources.description:
If You're Looking For Trouble... You Can Find It In This Man's Arms! 
Beautiful Mary returns from Chicago to her small hometown after many years, wearing a mink coat and carrying an expensive cigarette case. Her arrival causes long standing enmities to re-surface between two of her old boyfriends, leading to robbery and murder.
